Dr.Gopinath treated my teeth and gum issues holistically. I went in seeking a particular expensive cosmetic treatment but rather than push it on me, he was frank that I may not be the best candidate for it at this time. Instead, we decided to fix my bone loss and gum issues which I believe was the right problem to address first. The clinic is well-equipped  - X-rays, lasers etc. Their covid protocols are thorough - whole-body sanitization spray, feet covers, head covers, PPE, sanitization of the room after every patient - so I felt safe getting teeth-work done during the pandemic. I was also happy that the clinic was moderate-sized but clean, well-run and provided personalized care, and was not a massive commecial establishment where nameless doctors come and go. Side note: Dr. Gopinath has an impressive memory. He remembered that I had once visited him two years back and was able to recall my issue and history!
